  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; hash is present for content integrity but signature workflow is pending and no digital signature has been applied. Full 13-factor assessment carried forward from the Morrison framework. Decision record reflects Accepted outcome conditional on resolution of open credibility gaps in subsequent review cycle.",
